  "texts": [
    "Another interesting opinion shared had to do with the perceived cost of applying ethics in AI development.",
    "For example, too much ethical accountability was perceived as having a negative impact on business and organisational growth.",
    "A participant in [G6] stated: ɓ \"If I have to be very \"ethical\", accuracy will also be affected.",
    "Then I think there is a dilemma there, at the end, of how ethical I am and how much business I am losing.",
    "\"-AI practitioner-[G6]."
  ]
}